freenet.io
Class AddressTrackerItem

java.lang.Object
  freenet.io.AddressTrackerItem
Direct Known Subclasses:
InetAddressAddressTrackerItem, PeerAddressTrackerItem
public class AddressTrackerItem
extends Object

Tracks communication to/from a specific address. That address can be a specific IP:port, a specific IP, or some completely different type of address, so we don't store it in this class; subclasses will do.

Author:
toad
